posts.name: Fletch
posts.cooked:
The error is right at the top.  Its failing to parse the JSON file.

I don’t remember the exact limits offhand, but my guess is its having issues parsing the decimal value for your drive factor due to too many digits.

posts.cooked: i change just the deploy files and I think I changed the values ​​in accordance with the document. I posted the deploy folder on github in case you want to check it out. GitHub - FRC9232/yagsl-deploy
